    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1" facs="http://www.tapasproject.org/sites/default/files/1524006795/support_files/1912Aug17a.jpg"/> <!-- 1912Aug17a.jpg -->           
            <opener>
                <handShift new="#h2"/>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1912-08-17">Aug. 17" 1912</date>
                    <handShift new="#h1"/>
                    <name>Baymeath,</name>
                    <name>Bar Harbor, Maine.</name>                    
                </dateline>
                <salute><handShift new="#h2"/>Dear <persName ref="/sites/default/files/1524486624/tei/Annotations.xml#pers_edith_abbott">Miss Abbott</persName>,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I have written <persName ref="/sites/default/files/1524486624/tei/Annotations.xml#pers_esther_kohn">Esther</persName>
                that you are coming to
                Lakeside in Sept. probably
                the day she leaves Sept. 4th.
                I am so glad you are 
                going down. I do hope you
                will plan stay for the
                month.
            </p>
            <closer>
                <salute> Always affectionately yours</salute>
                <signed>
                    <persName ref="/sites/default/files/1524486624/tei/Annotations.xml#pers_jane_addams">Jane Addams</persName>
                </signed>
            </closer>  
            <pb n="2" facs="http://www.tapasproject.org/sites/default/files/1524006486/support_files/1912Aug17b.jpg"/><!-- 1912Aug17b.jpg -->
        </body> 
